# Known-flaky or expected-missing URLs to exclude from link checking.
# One pattern per line; supports regex.

# Placeholder/example URLs
https?://example\.com
https?://localhost

# CDN resources (may rate-limit CI)
https://cdnjs\.cloudflare\.com

# GitHub API rate limiting
https://api\.github\.com

# NuGet package pages (may return 404 for pre-release versions)
https://www\.nuget\.org/packages/.*/\d+\.\d+\.\d+-

# Playground (Blazor WASM, loaded client-side — not crawlable)
/playground/

# Live site URLs (may 404 before deployment or for pages not yet published)
https://corvus-oss\.org

# Source-code links in API docs point to main branch; 404 until feature branch is merged
https://github\.com/corvus-dotnet/Corvus\.JsonSchema/blob/main/src/
https://github\.com/corvus-dotnet/Corvus\.JsonSchema/blob/main/src-v4/
https://github\.com/corvus-dotnet/Corvus\.JsonSchema/blob/main/Common/

# Microsoft Docs generic interface member URLs that return 404
# (e.g. IEquatable.Equals, IEnumerator.Current — MS docs uses IEquatable-1.Equals)
https://learn\.microsoft\.com/dotnet/api/system\.iequatable\.equals
https://learn\.microsoft\.com/dotnet/api/system\.collections\.generic\.ienumerator\.current
https://learn\.microsoft\.com/dotnet/api/system\.collections\.generic\.ienumerable\.getenumerator
https://learn\.microsoft\.com/dotnet/api/system\.collections\.immutable\.immutablelist-1\+builder
https://learn\.microsoft\.com/dotnet/api/system\.text\.json\.jsonvaluekind\.undefined#undefined

# Truncated MS Docs URLs (lychee sometimes truncates long URLs during crawl)
https://learn\.microsoft\.com/do\.\.$
https://learn\.microsoft\.com/dotnet/ap\.\.$
https://learn\.microsoft\.com/dotnet/api/syste\.\.$

# Unversioned API type pages (XmlDocToMarkdown cross-references missing v4/ or v5/ prefix)
file:///.*api/corvus-

# V5 internal types excluded from API docs but still cross-referenced
file:///.*api/v5/corvus-text-json-internal-
file:///.*api/v5/corvus-text-json-jsonelement\.html$